<div class="post"{% if loop is defined and loop.last and offset is defined %} hx-indicator="#post-spinner" hx-get="/hx/list-posts?offset={{ offset }}" hx-trigger="intersect once" hx-swap="afterend"{% endif %}>
    <div class="card card-light mb-3 post-card">
        <a class="card-body" href="{{ path('app_view_post', { id: post.id })}}">
            <h2 class="card-title">{{ post.title }}</h2>
            {% if post.body is defined %}
                <p>{{ post.body }}</p>
            {% endif %}
        </a>
        <div class="card-body">
            <button id="hearts-{{ post.id }}" class="float-start border-0 bg-transparent{% if app.user and post.currentUserHearted %} text-danger{% else %} text-muted{% endif %} pe-3"{% if app.user %} onclick="toggleHeart({{ post.id }})"{% endif %}>
                <i class="bi bi-heart-fill"></i> <span class="heart-count">{{ post.heartCount }}</span>
            </button>
            <a class="text-muted" href="{{ path('app_view_post', { id: post.id })}}#comments">
                <i class="bi bi-chat-fill"></i> {{ post.commentCount }}
            </a>
            <div class="date float-end text-muted">{{ post.posted|time_diff }}</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
